 politics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aAmerican wit and humor. 0aInvectivezUnited States. 0aPolitical satire, AmericanxHistory and criticism. 0aSituation comedies (Television programs)zUnited StatesxHistory and criticism. 4aAmerica. 4aAmerican Studies. 4aCulture. 4aDisparagement. 4aHumor. 4aLiterary Studies. 4aLiterature. 4aPopular Culture. 4aSitcom. 4aUS Popular Culture. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / American / General.2bisacsh  aAmerica.  aAmerican Studies.  aCulture.  aDisparagement.  aHumor.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aPopular Culture.  aSitcom.  aUS Popular Culture.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2z978311076700108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022 Englishz978311099389908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2022z9783110994810oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022 Englishz978311099375208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022z9783110993738oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2022z9783111025094oZDB-23-TGP08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2022z978311076851040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978383946260740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839462607423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839462607/original  a978-3-11-076700-1  DG Plus PP Package 2022 Part 2b2022  a978-3-11-076851-0  transcript English Frontlist eBook-Package 2022b2022  a978-3-11-099375-2  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural, Area Studies 2022 Englishb2022  a978-3-11-099389-9  EBOOK PACKAGE COM